  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK930">
<l>kaḷḷuṇṇāp pōḻtiṟ kaḷittāṉaik kāṇuṅkāl </l>
<l> uḷḷāṉko luṇṭataṉ cōrvu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When (a drunkard) who is sober sees one who is not, it looks as if he remembered not the evil effects of his (own) drink.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
